item.title: CVE-2023-0105|2023-01-13T04:22:02.451274Z -- redhat.com -- keycloak
item.description: A flaw was found in Keycloak. This flaw allows impersonation and lockout due to the email trust not being handled correctly in Keycloak. An attacker can shadow other users with the same email and lockout or impersonate them.
